Much of my work involves audio systems as a tool for other things than sound.
http://youtu.be/F0WSTMX9TJo

This simple board allows you to have two computer controlled flexible PWM outputs.
It simply hooks up to your sound card. Generate square waves to control the things.
PureData offers a flexible environment to conduct your experiments.
Record your creations to sound files and play them back with whatever :)
